name: CITY 01 - Streets in Little Nostalgia
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection located in Kitty City in the Little Nostalgia neighborhood.
This image shows a top view of the neighborhood center, where the location of the main square surrounded by hotels, restaurants, cafes and services can be seen. Sounds and music arise that intermingle in the streets, at night they are embellished with the lights of the oldest prominent buildings in the city.
